sequenceDiagram
  participant UI as Frontend AG-UI
  participant API as Agent Service
  participant Val as SQL Validator
  participant DB as Cloud SQL scoped views
  participant LLM as LLM Core / Vertex
  participant Tools as Tool Registry

  UI->>API: user message / run
  API->>LLM: build prompt with scoped context
  LLM-->>API: tool call or answer
  API->>Tools: authorize tool by scope
  alt SQL tool
    Tools->>Val: validate SELECT-only and allowlist
    Val->>DB: SET LOCAL ROLE + tenant GUCs + statement_timeout
    DB-->>Tools: bounded result
  else mutating/sensitive tool
    Tools-->>API: require gate/approval
  end
  API-->>UI: AG-UI events / SSE with timeout

